summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing the preparation of plans, specifications and cost estimates for the rehabilitation of the Fourth Avenue South viaduct, South Jackson Street to Airport Way South; authorizing an agreement with the State of Washington, Department of Highways, providing for financial aid under the Federal Aid "M" Program, Federal Aid Highway Act of 1970, and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Seattle General Street Improvement Bonds 1960 Fund therefor.
